No. 303,

Misc., October Term, 1966.

No. 528. Curry v. United States, Berguido et al. v. Eastern Airlines, Inc.,

385 U. S. 873, 387 U. S. 949; and

390 U. S. 996, 391 U. S. 909. Motions for leave to file second petitions for rehearing denied.

Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of these motions.
